title: Queen + Adam Lambert - Summer Sonic, Tokyo, Japan - 17th August
description:
Queen + Adam Lambert - Summer Sonic, Tokyo, Japan - 17th August 2014 MultiCam

Mp4 H.264 1920 x 1080 SD

This one was difficult to produce due to a lack of decent camera angles. This concert took place in a Marine Park (field) with no seating, so the camera work is not as impressive as the recent USA gigs. With that said the people who did film this did a great job considering the environment they were in.
